## Core Principles

* **DRY (Don't Repeat Yourself)**: Single source of truth, reference other files
* **Token Effective**: Concise, avoid redundancy, use references
* **Single Responsibility**: Each MDC file has one clear purpose
* **Always Updated**: Keep `.cursor/rules/` files current
* **English Only**: Always write documentation in English, even when user asks in other languages

